channel.title: Ever noticed this screen shot? {Death Race}
channel.description:
Haha. I was bored today while botting, so I decided to get the torrent Death Race, before I watch DR2, and as I was watching it I saw this part and was like holyyyyy shit. Hah
Well I thought it was fairly cool. I know the movie is like 5/10 maybe. Was just wondering if anyone else noticed it. I think the reason why I did so fast, was because of the "M", but as you can tell some letters are missing.
[URL=http://img689.imageshack.us/i/moparr.jpg/][IMG]http://img689.imageshack.us/img689/8379/moparr.jpg[/img][/URL]
